fcc_flb
====================================================================================================
Description:
    This test does some basic checking of synchronization using FCC and FLB. 
    test0: All enabled HART(s) in a shire participate on an FLB and then wait for an FCC
           credit. The last HART that reaches the FCC, unlocks all the HART(s).
    test1: Same as test0 but instead of using a single FLB, the test use
           2 FLBs (odd and even harts). Last Odd/Even HART unlock the others of the same
           type

Parametrization:
    -DOVER_PARAMS: Enables parametrization
    -DSHIRE_MASK: et-dvrun-style mask with the shires where should run the test
    -DMINION_MASK: et-dvrun-style mask with the minions in a shire that should run the test
    -DTHREAD_MASK: et-dvrun-style mask with the threads in a minion that should run the test

